Describes spatial or conceptual relationships between objects within an artwork. The specific relationships are specified using the rdfs:subPropertyOf.
                Examples:
                - Spatial relation: :cup_object arto:rests_on :table_object ;
                  arto:rests_on rdfs:subPropertyOf arto:relatedTo;
                - Interaction: :mother_figure arto:holds :child_figure ;
                  arto:holds rdfs:subPropertyOf arto:relatedTo;
                - Position: :cloud_object arto:above :mountain_object ;
                  arto:above rdfs:subPropertyOf arto:relatedTo

Indicates that an event relatedToConnotation some connotations.
                Examples:
                  ex:NoahDoveEvent rdf:type arto:Event ;
                  arto:relatedToConnotation ex:PeaceSymbolism ;
